-- Publicis Aims to Increase Dividend Payout, CEO Tells Investir
-- B y   F a b i o   B e n e d e t t i - V a l e n t i n i
-- 2012-07-21T10:07:13Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-07-21/publicis-aims-to-increase-dividend-payout-ceo-tells-investir.html
Publicis Groupe SA will
“gradually” increase its dividend payout toward 35 percent to
40 percent of annual earnings, compared with 23.6 percent for
2011, Chief Executive Officer  Maurice Levy  told French weekly
newspaper  Investir  in an interview. Levy didn’t give a timeframe
for the dividend payout hikes, according to the Investir
interview.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Fabio Benedetti-Valentini in Paris at 
